Class Resource

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xing.api.Resource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BookmarksResource, ContactsResource, GroupsResource, JobsResource, MessagesResource, MiscellaneousResource, ProfileEditingResource, ProfileVisitsResource, RecommendationsResource, UserProfilesResource

    public abstract class Resource
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for all resources that provide access to various XING api endpoints.
